    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle in good condition, perfect for anyone looking for a reliable and comfortable ride. The engine runs smoothly and all major systems are in solid working order, having received regular servicing. While the interior is clean and smoke-free, the exterior shows some light signs of use consistent with its age, such as minor stone chips on the hood. Overall, this is a dependable car that offers great value and is ready for its next owner.",
