    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great with only minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful driving, while the interior is clean with some gentle wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. You can expect a reliable, comfortable ride that presents very well for its age.",
