      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, retaining its deep, factory-fresh luster. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and unscratched, and every electronic component functions with precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. This is more than just a pre-owned car; it is a collector-grade example that drives with the same tightness and responsiveness as the day it was delivered. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
